        "text": "I  called  this  meeting   today in order  to discuss   our  manufacturing plan.    As   I'm   sure   you're  all  aware,    with   the   credit crunch,   and  the  global financial crisis,   we're   obligated   to look  for   more cost efficient  ways  of   producing   our    goods.    We   don't   want  to have  to be  looking  at  redundancies.   So,    we've   outlined   a  brief   plan   to implement  the   just-in-time  philosophy."
