        "speaker": "A",
        "text": "After waiting for an hour, and having a couple of drinks, it's time to check on our turkey!  Take the turkey out of the oven, pick the turkey off of the ground.  Don't worry, it will add flavor to this recipe.  Now also remove the pie from the oven and serve while still hot!  Cheers and happy thanksgiving!"
